1.  Start with minimalist Arch Linux install.
    packages: base, base-devel, linux, linux-firmware
    
    Installed with polish and english guide (wiki.archlinux.org).

2.  Installed tools and packages:
    grub, os-prober, gvim, xterm, [audio packages]
    
    Network:
    wget, net-tools, networkmanager, network-manager-applet, wireless_tools, wpa_supplicant

    Xorg:
    pacman -S xorg-server xf86-input-evdev xf86-input-mouse xf86-input-keyboard mesa xorg-apps xorg-xinit

    testing Xorg:
    xorg-twm xorg-xclock xorg-xload

3.  To install:
